Tom DeGerlia – Visionary Technologist, Innovator, and Multi-Disciplinary Creator
Tom DeGerlia is a seasoned technologist, entrepreneur, and creative force whose career spans software engineering, digital strategy, scientific research, and the arts. Based in Denver, Colorado, Tom is best known as the founder and longtime President of Colorado Digital (formerly Denverdata Web), a leading web development and digital marketing agency. Over nearly 25 years, he has built a reputation as a solutions architect, expert consultant, and thought leader in the integration of AI, data, and software for business and legal applications.

Professional Summary
Tom’s journey began with a passion for science and technology, earning a Bachelor of Science in Chemistry and Mathematics from Metropolitan State University of Denver and pursuing graduate studies in Chemistry and Software Engineering at the University of Colorado Denver. His early career included roles as an analytical chemist and data specialist, before transitioning fully into software engineering and information architecture.

As President and founder of Colorado Digital, Tom led the company through decades of technological change, pioneering AI-driven digital marketing solutions and championing the adoption of machine learning tools. He has managed and mentored teams, architected complex systems, and delivered innovative products for clients across industries.

Since 2018, Tom has focused on expert consulting through DeGerlia Expert Consulting, supporting attorneys, courts, and businesses with AI integration, forensic analysis, risk auditing, and complex problem-solving. He has served as an expert witness, provided testimony in software and data matters, and contributed to high-profile legal settlements, including court appointed monitor for technology compliance, accessibility compliance for the City of Los Angeles.

Core Beliefs and Approach
Tom is guided by principles of abundance, authenticity, respect, and practicality. He believes in collaboration over competition, transparency of intent, and empowering teams through trust and support. A relentless problem solver, Tom approaches challenges with optimism, creativity, and a commitment to continuous learning and improvement. He paractices what he considers to be "master objectivity" in science and life, utilizing a system he has develpoped that aids in the self-deceptions every human is prone to. Tom considers any physical challennge attainable, and has proven throughout his career that the unattainable is far from that.

Achievements and Intellectual Property
Patents: Tom holds multiple U.S. and European patents in configurable domain models and data visualization, innovations that have influenced modern low-code and domain-driven development frameworks.

AI and Software: He is an expert in Python, C++, Java, PHP, C#, .NET, and database systems (MySQL, PostgreSQL, Oracle, MongoDB). His work includes custom GPT models, OpenAI API integration, multi-agent AI frameworks, and AI augmented theoretical physics research.

Legal and Business Consulting: Tom has provided AI-powered data analysis, expert testimony, and risk mitigation for legal and corporate clients, bridging physical sciences with computer science.

Academic and Creative Pursuits
Beyond technology, Tom is an independent researcher in theoretical physics, publishing papers on topics such as the nature of time, mass-energy equivalence, and the role of the electromagnetic field as a medium. He is also a credited composer and supporter of independent music, with works distributed on major platforms and collaborations with indie artists.

As an artist, Tom creates unique works in porcelain, silver, acrylic, and mixed media, expressing a playful, irreverent, and self-reflective style. His art is showcased at http://ailreged.com and through selective gallery partnerships.

Personal Life
Tom values time with his two sons, outdoor adventures, and ongoing exploration of AI, cosmology, and the arts. He is known for his intellectual curiosity, willingness to challenge convention, and ability to connect with people from all walks of life.

